        "icon_ATijJh": {
          "type": "icon",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "shopify://shop_images/Group_96_1_ecca9e05-273a-42b8-9919-cfcc7eb42e6d.png",
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>We are certified <a href=\"/pages/4ocean-partnership\" title=\"/pages/4ocean-partnership\"><strong>4Ocean</strong></a> cleanup partners! With our Buy 1 to Pull 1 partnership, we have helped remove 429,232 pounds of plastic and trash from the ocean, rivers, and coastlines— that’s the equivalent of 3,863,079 shampoo bottles or 17.1 Million Water bottles worth of plastic!</p>",
            "use_custom_style": false,
            "border_color": "",
            "bg_color": "",
            "title_color": "",
            "text_bg": ""
          }
        },
        "icon_nHjMt7": {
          "type": "icon",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "shopify://shop_images/Group_98.png",
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>Taking water out of products like shampoo, conditioner, and body wash cuts down on shipping weight and volume, which helps to reduce carbon emissions and packing from production to consumption.</p>",
            "use_custom_style": false,
            "border_color": "",
            "bg_color": "",
            "title_color": "",
            "text_bg": ""
          }
        },
        "icon_VgUUBz": {
          "type": "icon",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "shopify://shop_images/Group_99.png",
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>Globally, we produce twice as much plastic packaging waste than we did 20 years ago. The vast majority of this waste ends up in landfills, where it takes up to 450 years to decompose.</p>",
            "use_custom_style": false,
            "border_color": "",
            "bg_color": "",
            "title_color": "",
            "text_bg": ""
          }
        },
        "icon_GVBQK9": {
          "type": "icon",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "shopify://shop_images/Group_100.png",
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>98% of Kitsch products come in paper packaging. It’s our go-to packaging material because it has lower carbon emissions and it’s recyclable.</p>",
            "use_custom_style": false,
            "border_color": "",
            "bg_color": "",
            "title_color": "",
            "text_bg": ""
          }
        },
        "icon_39Cier": {
          "type": "icon",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "shopify://shop_images/Group_2_4.png",
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>In an effort to support new and emerging projects in underserved communities, we have partnered with Charity Water to build a community well in Uganda that will provide clean water access to over 300 community members.</p>",
            "use_custom_style": false,
